    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six maintains optimal compression across all cylinders, with the double VANOS system recently overhauled for precision valve timing. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagements, delivering torque through a factory limited-slip differential. Chassis integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and tuned dampers to preserve original kinematics. Finished in a flawless coat with zero oxidation, this specimen retains its factory torsional rigidity and visceral, naturally aspirated throttle response.",
      "price": 44500.0,
