      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence that must be seen to be believed. This vehicle is in pristine showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes, and is further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to a cabin that still carries a hint of that new-car aroma; the premium leather upholstery is supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and every piece of interior trim is flawless. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified specialists. Every electronic feature, switch, and sensor operates with factory precision. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the dealership floor.",
