      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and there isn't a single scratch or blemish to be found. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
