    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically superlative E46 M3, this S54-powered icon is in investment-grade condition. The 3.2L straight-six features a fully overhauled double-VANOS system and proactive rod bearing replacement, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and reliability. The chassis has been professionally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points and upgraded with Bilstein B16 coilovers for sharpened turn-in and roll control. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Zero fluid leaks, impeccable compression across all cylinders, and a flawless undercarriage make this a definitive enthusiast's example.",
